{"tid":2099053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「互聯網訊息審核員」成中國新工種","createTime":"2020-07-08T03:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T03:25:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e91e55591ec4f46d791a0fcfb3b8f8cca4ca339","tid":2099053,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200708/JW3VGTJI6JZUG6AOMMI62VUGMY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200708%2FJW3VGTJI6JZUG6AOMMI62VUGMY%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK9AAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=713beb65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200708%2FJW3VGTJI6JZUG6AOMMI62VUGMY%2F&h=7ecaac6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200708/JW3VGTJI6JZUG6AOMMI62VUGMY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「互聯網訊息審核員」成中國新工種<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s8oWKN-r4Q-6s1kOIb9SQDhKFJE=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KYW2VNHT22BWDCVZVAEBTFFLBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs8oWKN-r4Q-6s1kOIb9SQDhKFJE%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKYW2VNHT22BWDCVZVAEBTFFLBQ.jpg&h=9f132641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共的網絡監控體系再一步擴大。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中共箝制思想及言論，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n當局表示，網審員的工作將越來越重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需具辨別「有害」訊息能力<br />\n<br />\n人力資源社會保障部官網前日發佈，「中華人民共和國職業分類大典（2015年版）」新增了「信息安全測試員」、「互聯網營銷師」等九個新職業。此次還加入了「互聯網訊息審核員」、「直播銷售員」等五個工種。據悉，新職業具有以下三個特點：一是協助防控武漢肺炎疫情，凸顯相關職業的重要性；二是互聯網技術發展，催生多樣化創業就業模式；三是訊息技術發展，對網絡信用及安全提出新要求。據報，當局要求網審員具備辨別「有害」訊息的能力，亦要有豐富而全面的知識，執行力強，性格細心、耐心等。<br />\n<br />\n通報指出，<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n連同今次的新公佈，2019年以來，國家已經公佈三批共38個新職業。<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n微信"},{"pid":"4dc96fd9f27ebbc38b2231d5db1fe422af9181e0","tid":2099053,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"我想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f4480d97b999ee75f5dd4c3d94313a8b1d6a66","tid":2099053,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"坐最近嗰條友都似比人洗咗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2ecef1febd144fbb6099393e489f28d86c5983","tid":2099053,"uid":293307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:25:20.000Z","msg":"幾錢一個月？定5毛一個Post？"}]}